snippet.title: ILLURAMA: Masters of Illusions | SAGE DEMO sample
snippet.description:
Hi, this is a sample of what you can find in this demo. This is a bullet hell platformer, so you will jump and dodge a lot of bullets!. Only the first stage in this demo.
DOWNLOAD HERE:
https://sonicfangameshq.com/forums/showcase/illurama-masters-of-illusions-demo.2293/
https://yenfay.itch.io/illurama-masters-of-ilusions
